    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Jesse Watters wants to pretend the end of Roe is no big deal. Reality keeps proving him wrong\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/15/22 8:55 AM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/jesse-watters/jesse-watters-repeatedly-fails-efforts-suppress-critical-reporting-ohio-ten-year-old"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Fox used Biden's ill-advised trip to Saudi Arabia to continue its unwavering support for the fossil fuel industry\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/19/22 12:28 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/fox-news-used-president-joe-bidens-ill-advised-trip-saudi-arabia-continue-its-unwavering"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      These media figures discredited a report on a 10-year-old girl needing an abortion. There was just an arrest in the case.\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Research/Study\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/13/22 5:06 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/these-media-figures-discredited-report-10-year-old-girl-needing-medical-abortion-there-was"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Laura Ingraham\u2019s reaction to her friend Pat Cipollone\u2019s testimony shows how Fox was complicit in Trump's coup\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/13/22 1:14 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/january-6-insurrection/laura-ingrahams-reaction-her-friend-pat-cipollones-testimony-shows-how-fox"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      In the first half of 2022, Fox News feverishly pushed debunked, racist, and inflammatory narratives about immigration and migrants \n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/12/22 1:52 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
