    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      At every step of the way, right-wing media provided the pretext for Trump\u2019s attempted coup\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  09/24/21 1:10 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/january-6-insurrection/every-step-way-right-wing-media-provided-pretext-trumps-attempted-coup"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      The evolution of Tucker Carlson's January 6 conspiracy mongering\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Research/Study\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  02/15/22 10:20 AM EST\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/evolution-tucker-carlsons-january-6-conspiracy-mongering-0"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Facebook\u2019s failures with election misinformation contributed to the deadly Capitol insurrection. A year later, the platform has failed to fix its problems.\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Research/Study\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  01/05/22 5:37 PM EST\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/january-6-insurrection/facebooks-failures-election-misinformation-contributed-deadly-capitol"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Fox hosts downplay Trump\u2019s culpability for the insurrection -- and their own\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  02/11/21 12:59 PM EST\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/fox-hosts-downplay-trumps-culpability-insurrection-and-their-own"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Leading up to January 6, Steve Bannon publicly bragged about his behind-the-scene role fomenting the insurrection\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  10/29/21 10:25 AM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/steve-bannon/leading-january-6-steve-bannon-publicly-bragged-about-his-behind-scene-role-fomenting"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      In 2 weeks after it called the election, Fox News cast doubt on the results nearly 800 times\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  01/14/21 2:52 PM EST\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/2-weeks-after-it-called-election-fox-news-cast-doubt-results-nearly-800-times"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      These are Fox News' leading advertisers\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  07/26/19 1:37 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/these-are-fox-news-leading-advertisers"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      These are Tucker Carlson\u2019s leading advertisers\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  12/19/18 12:00 PM EST\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/these-are-tucker-carlsons-leading-advertisers"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      These are Laura Ingraham's leading advertisers\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  10/29/19 12:15 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/these-are-laura-ingrahams-leading-advertisers"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Elon Musk\u2019s plan to reinstate Trump on Twitter would just reignite a race to the bottom\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  05/10/22 2:44 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/elon-musk/elon-musk-says-he-would-reverse-twitters-ban-donald-trump"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Emboldened by Musk\u2019s Twitter takeover, anti-trans figures are celebrating by breaking the platform\u2019s rules on hateful conduct\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  05/04/22 11:17 AM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/elon-musk/emboldened-musks-twitter-takeover-anti-trans-figures-are-celebrating-breaking-platforms"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Mainstream coverage adopts Elon Musk\u2019s \u201cfree speech\u201d framing \u2013 despite his anti-union, anti-speech, anti-worker history\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  04/25/22 8:02 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/twitter/mainstream-coverage-adopts-elon-musks-free-speech-framing-despite-his-anti-union-anti"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      Elon Musk's own Twitter use is the biggest sign he's unfit to steer the ship\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Research/Study\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  04/25/22 6:31 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/elon-musk/elon-musks-own-twitter-use-biggest-sign-hes-unfit-steer-ship"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      With the platform's board agreeing to Elon Musk's bid, power now rests with Twitter\u2019s advertisers\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  04/25/22 4:08 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/twitter/platforms-board-agreeing-elon-musks-bid-power-now-rests-twitters-advertisers"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      With attack on Twitter, the right shows it has institutionalized Trump\u2019s corrupt use of government power\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Article\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  04/25/22 12:55 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/donald-trump/attack-twitter-right-shows-it-has-institutionalized-trumps-corrupt-use-government"
    },
    {
      "text": "Abortion Rights & Reproductive Health",
      "url": "/abortion-rights-and-reproductive-health"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n    \n      \n              \n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n          \n  \n\n    \n      How right-wing media reacted to the Supreme Court overturning Roe v. Wade\n\n\n      \n\n\n      \n        \n          Narrative/Timeline\n    \n    \n  \n\n    \n  \n  06/24/22 6:42 PM EDT\n\n    \n  ",
      "url": "/fox-news/how-right-wing-media-reacted-supreme-court-overturning-roe-v-wade"
    },
